    "attributes": {
      "name": "Virtual Try-On Application",
      "summary": "The Virtual Try-On App is a photo-realistic digital fitting room that allows users to visualize how different garments and accessories look on their body using uploaded images or models. Its primary purpose is to enable virtual outfit experimentation by combining selected garments onto a user's body, generating realistic images from multiple angles, and providing interactive features such as model linking, garment customization, and image export. It supports real-time outfit composition, AI-powered image generation of different views, and managing a library of garments and models, all within a responsive, user-friendly interface.",
